## Coral Studio Integration

The MCP adapter provides these tools to Coral Studio:

1. **get_price(symbol)** ‚Üí Returns real-time price data from multiple APIs
2. **analyze_market(symbol, horizon, provider)** ‚Üí AI-powered market analysis with RAG context
3. **feed_oracle(symbol)** ‚Üí Posts price data to Solana devnet oracle
4. **health()** ‚Üí System health status (no auth required)

### Tool Schemas (for Studio registration)

```typescript
